<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-04 01:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3393 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BKN-RHODEN-COLUMN-1ST     06-04 0685
