</P>
<P>
   7. Would you be willing to go on a lame ``reunion tour'' in
about four years?
</P>
<P>
   6. Do you have another job lined up when we fire your ass?
</P>
<P>
   5. Were you dumb enough to spend $9 on a ticket for the Spice
Girls movie?
</P>
<P>
   4. Oh, and by the way, can you, like, sing or anything?
</P>
<P>
