<DOCNO> NYT19980604.0281 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-04 19:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4647 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SUN-FINANCIAL-EARLY-B     06-04 0748
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SUN-FINANCIAL-EARLY-BUDGET-NYT </SLUG>
  
