<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MOTHER-EARTH-THE-BIG-PICTURE-NYTSF </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   How healthy is our planet's biodiversity?
</P>
<P>
   ...................................
</P>
<P>
   ..............O....................
</P>
<P>
   .......OO......O..OO..O............
</P>
<P>
   ......OO........OOO...O.....OO.....
</P>
<P>
   .......OO....OO.OO....OO..OO.......
</P>
<P>
   ..OO....OO....OO....OO..OO.........
</P>
<P>
   ....OO...OOO...OO.OO...OO..O....OO.
