orphaned children gathered to pay their last respects and eulogize
the slain star, a week after he was shot to death by his wife, who
then committed suicide. Among those at the suburban Glendale
cemetery were 9-year-old Sean Edward Hartman and 6-year-old Birgen
Anika Hartman. By Jesse Hiestand. (Will move in the ``a'' national
and ``n'' California news files.)
</P>
<P>
   STUDENT-BADGES (Los Angeles) _ If Antelope Valley Union High
School District trustee Bill Olenick gets his way, local high
school students would all wear photo ID badges at school. Olenick
says it would help teachers and other staff members _ who would get
their own badges _ identify students and make it easier to spot
outsiders. By Karen Maeshiro. (Will move in the ``a'' national and
``n'' California news files.)
