   BBA-COLUMN-THIEL (Salt Lake City) The jokers who said Karl
Malone and John Stockton were too old two years ago when the Sonics
ousted them en route to the NBA Finals are eating crow now.
</P>
<P>
   By Art Thiel. (story will move in the ``s'' category)
