<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-ALBANIA-KOSOVO-NYT, which moved
in ``i'' news file.) 
c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``People are trying to hang on, desperately hoping that the
world will intervene to save them. We could not hold out any
longer. There are thousands more behind us. Once they realize there
is no hope they will follow.''
</P>
<P>
   _BESIM ALIAJ, an ethnic Albanian refugee.
</P>
</TEXT>
