<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-04 21:38 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4956 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NEUTRINO-MASS-BOS &LR;      06-04 0773
