<HEADLINE>
KENNETH STARR'S OBSESSION WITH A FIVE-LETTER WORD  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This excellent 1,050-word ``separate buy'' article is from the
current (week beginning 6 June 1998) Economist magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
